    "description": "<strong>永恒的轮回开始了，每一个新的开始都是挑战。</strong><br>在 Eternal Rising 中，你必须不断变强才能生存。这是一款类 Rogue 弹幕游戏，无情的敌人会在每一步阻挡你。唯一的选择就是不断前进，摧毁一切挡在路上的东西。死亡是不可避免的——但每一次尝试都会让你进化，变得更强大，更好地准备迎接永生的无尽考验。<br><br><strong>在 Eternal Rising 中战斗穿越独特的世界</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292870/extras/0d81a34d0914bbf8baa22bde122c2244.poster.avif?t=1759234380\" width=615 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292870/extras/0d81a34d0914bbf8baa22bde122c2244.webm?t=1759234380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>收集经验球，释放强力攻击，粉碎敌人。从各种武器和精心调整的升级中选择，每次冒险都能定制你的构建。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292870/extras/a27768207c994daf9ce8bfb61c45f8a9.poster.avif?t=1759234380\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292870/extras/a27768207c994daf9ce8bfb61c45f8a9.webm?t=1759234380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292870/extras/a27768207c994daf9ce8bfb61c45f8a9.mp4?t=1759234380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在 Eternal Rising 中，规则很简单：升起或陨落。利用一切工具击败敌人，在这段无情的类 Rogue 冒险中开辟通向胜利的道路。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292870/extras/f3d1c6740a0a26a2341fb8a276b99166.poster.avif?t=1759234380\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292870/extras/f3d1c6740a0a26a2341fb8a276b99166.webm?t=1759234380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292870/extras/f3d1c6740a0a26a2341fb8a276b99166.mp4?t=1759234380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>击败守护者 Boss，解锁通往下一个领域的通道。为史诗般的对决做好准备，一次胜利一次胜利地开拓未知。",
